<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/60844029-cory-sheldon">Cory Sheldon</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m finding I just need to really be awake due to it&apos;s very meandering quality. Certainly not a fast read in that way, also, not a great book to read <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm finding I just need to really be awake due to it's very meandering quality. Certainly not a fast read in that way, also, not a great book to read in bed when I'm sleepy. I do find it pretty engaging if I'm wide awake, though.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
